|     kernel img region     |
+---------------------------+ <-- end (kernel.ld 导出)
|    page_metadata region   |  # struct page 数组
+---------------------------+ <-- START_MEM (0xa4000000)
|          MEMORY           |
|           ...             |
+---------------------------+ <-- PHYSTOP (0x80000000 + 3GB)
```

